# Default-deny the build context so local data and scratch outputs never get sent
# to Docker unless we explicitly need them.
**

!.dockerignore
!Dockerfile
!README.md
!LICENSE
!environment.yml
!setup.py
!deid/
!deid/**
!deidecho_run/
!deidecho_run/**

# Exclude Python bytecode/caches inside otherwise-included trees.
**/__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/**
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/*.pyd

# Exclude development-only content inside otherwise-included trees.
deid/tests/
deid/tests/**
